first_tick_commands: execute as @s unless score @s satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.unlock.skill.tree matches 0.. run scoreboard players set @s satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.unlock.skill.tree 1

commands: execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.interaction=2..}] as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.interaction=2..}] run scoreboard players reset @s satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.interaction

first_tick_commands: execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.night.vision=1}] run tag @s add night_vision
last_tick_commands: execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.night.vision=2}] run tag @s remove night_vision
execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.night.vision=2..}] run scoreboard players reset @s satsu.iron.man.addon.ia.night.vision
execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.scan.enemies=2..}] run scoreboard players reset @s satsu.iron.man.scan.enemies
execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.energy.ia.unlock.icon.in.hud=2..}] run scoreboard players reset @s satsu.iron.man.addon.energy.ia.unlock.icon.in.hud

commands: execute as @s[scores={satsu.iron.man.addon.enable.sentinel=2..}] run scoreboard players reset @s satsu.iron.man.addon.enable.sentinel
